Package grammars.FOOL

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    FOOLVisitor<T>
    This interface defines a complete generic visitor for a parse tree produced by FOOLParser.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    FOOLBaseVisitor<T>
    This class provides an empty implementation of FOOLVisitor, which can be extended to create a visitor which only needs to handle a subset of the available methods.
